<subSubSection id="C350B2B199218553E887FEFAD719F199" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99218553E887FEFAD76DF171" blockId="39.[151,1436,260,503]" box="[151,572,260,287]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899218553E887FEFAD743F171" bold="true" box="[151,530,260,287]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Number of specimens recorded.</emphasis>
44.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99218553E8D7FED7D02CF12D" blockId="39.[151,1436,260,503]" box="[199,1405,296,323]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899218553E8D7FED7D430F12D" bold="true" box="[199,353,296,323]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Distribution.</emphasis>
Rather restricted to western and southwestern Europe. 
<collectingCountry id="F35DA1AA99218553EBDCFED6D17EF12D" box="[972,1071,297,323]" name="Portugal" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Portugal</collectingCountry>
: five northernmost provinces.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99218553E8D7FEB2D730F1C1" blockId="39.[151,1436,260,503]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899218553E8D7FEB2D47DF109" bold="true" box="[199,300,333,359]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Ecology.</emphasis>
Most often collected in grassland and heathland biotopes, and thus far not observed in the littoral zone, dunes nor mountains. In northwestern Europe, this species is mainly found in humid to rather humid forests, and wooded swamps (or carrs) (
<bibRefCitation id="EFDB9CCB99218553E9DEFE6AD704F1C1" author="Pollet, M." box="[462,597,405,431]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" pagination="1 - 190" refId="ref34362" refString="Pollet, M. (2000) A documented Red List of the dolichopodid flies (Diptera: Dolichopodidae) of Flanders [in Dutch with English summary]. Communications of the Institute of Nature Conservation, 8, 1 - 190." type="journal article" year="2000">Pollet 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99218553E8D7FE47D79BF1BD" blockId="39.[151,1436,260,503]" box="[199,714,440,467]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899218553E8D7FE47D400F1BD" bold="true" box="[199,337,440,467]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Rarity (%).</emphasis>
10.3 (common). Fairly rare (FL).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99218553E8D7FE23D719F199" blockId="39.[151,1436,260,503]" box="[199,584,476,503]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899218553E8D7FE23D4D3F199" bold="true" box="[199,386,476,503]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Activity period.</emphasis>
May–September.
</paragraph>
